plot: Batwoman's hands are full as she juggles Jada's demands, Mary's ever-increasing power and a new romantic entanglement; Batwoman races against the clock to once again save the city and those closest to her.

The Bat Team race to save the Gotham Dam from Pam, and free Mary from the villainess' control, before it's too late. Meanwhile, Batwoman negotiates with Jada but fails to uphold her end of the bargain. And Hell hath no fury like a woman scorned.—Gislef
